    "description": "你因无罪之罪被判处在迷宫中死刑。米诺陶在原始时代建造了迷宫。曾被视为埃雷斯的终极监狱，这个结构发生了可怕的事情。作为幸存者，发现恐怖的怪物和严酷的实验，或者隐藏的绿洲和被遗忘的城市。寻找分享同样命运的盟友或敌人。小心，并不是每个人都为你的最佳利益着想。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/784753d9d07feb9159a48da2c039dd12.poster.avif?t=1760677606\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/784753d9d07feb9159a48da2c039dd12.webm?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>回合制战斗: </strong><br>战术性地决定如何部署队员。记住，一旦部署，那个单位将固定在战斗序列中。单位的部署方式将大大影响即将到来的冲突。选择施放、攻击和防御的内容。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/b523dc1429d946ba95aec25f99487d31.poster.avif?t=1760677606\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/b523dc1429d946ba95aec25f99487d31.webm?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/b523dc1429d946ba95aec25f99487d31.mp4?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>选择你的路径:</strong><br>法典可以稳定迷宫的部分，但无法保持每个墓穴的一致。决定走哪条路。更多的怪物、战利品、谜团还是废墟？寻找迷宫的邪恶怪物。掠夺更多的装备，发现亿万年前遗留下来的东西。发现失败的实验或定居点。揭开失落的秘密，或古代城市的部分。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/af486e5c1012da790622d351ecffbf8e.poster.avif?t=1760677606\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/af486e5c1012da790622d351ecffbf8e.webm?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/af486e5c1012da790622d351ecffbf8e.mp4?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>发现不同的生态区:</strong><br>迷宫充满了各种曲折。准备在不同的景观中战斗！在充满生命和植物的原始丛林中战斗。漫步在黑暗潮湿的洞穴中，那里有矿物、植物和隐藏的隧道，生物可能潜伏其中。发现古老的埃雷斯建筑，古老世界的奇迹仍然屹立。随着开发的进行，将宣布更多的生态区。<br><br><strong>创建你自己的地牢:</strong><br>与法典同步，学习稳定房间。创建独特的地牢布局，混合和匹配敌人、生物群系、照明等——任何可以想象的东西！迷宫已被用于实验多年，现在轮到你了。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/7c0e2172e5cf3da1aeb3b73cdf9de29f.poster.avif?t=1760677606\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/7c0e2172e5cf3da1aeb3b73cdf9de29f.webm?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/7c0e2172e5cf3da1aeb3b73cdf9de29f.mp4?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>前方有故事:</strong><br>发现丢失的笔记、地标、回声和实验。每个地牢都有新的任务，可能会在赛雷娜镇解锁新的故事线。艾达的林地将是完成笔记并为真正渴望传说的人提供更多故事的资源丰富的地点。每次任务后都要和你的同伴交谈——他们可能会有新的任务、奖励或情报给你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/33f2be70eeaef02606328ad988eee660.poster.avif?t=1760677606\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/33f2be70eeaef02606328ad988eee660.webm?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/33f2be70eeaef02606328ad988eee660.mp4?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>深化你的关系: </strong><br>在迷宫中独自生存是不可能的。在赛雷娜镇找到的每个同伴都会有新的任务线可以探索。在这些地狱般的大厅中，每个人都有一个目的，来到这里之前每个人都有自己的生活。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/ecca6062205fcee60aacbed3189779e5.poster.avif?t=1760677606\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/ecca6062205fcee60aacbed3189779e5.webm?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067460/extras/ecca6062205fcee60aacbed3189779e5.mp4?t=1760677606\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>游戏特点: </strong><br>•\t与队员一起发现独特的故事线。<br>•\t根据你的游戏风格选择哪个地牢目标，或玩所有可用的目标！<br>•\t一旦你收集到足够的地牢块，就可以开始编辑现有的地牢——或者不编辑。选择是你的。<br>•\t打造你的角色。从三个不同的职业中选择：战士、法师和盗贼。<br>•\t在回合制风格的网格中战术性地部署你的单位。<br>•\t收集材料并制作：护甲、武器、药水和药剂。<br><br><br>在迷宫中生存足够长的时间，揭开这些被遗弃大厅的原始魔法，并发现古代种族打算永远埋藏的恐怖。",
